1. Introduction

Automatically generated from <http://www.w3.org/2002/01/tr-automation/tr.rdf> using <http://greenbytes.de/tech/webdav/rfc2629xslt/gen-w3c-reference.xslt>.

Note that the ordering of authors is determined by retrieving the spec text and checking for the first occurance of the full author name. This may sometimes fail. If you find incorrect orderings, please notify julian.reschke@gmx.de.
